-- Whitbread Has No Plans to Spin Off Costa, CEO Harrison Says
-- B y   C o l m   H e a t l e y
-- 2012-06-19T07:17:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-19/whitbread-has-no-plans-to-spin-off-costa-ceo-harrison-says.html
Whitbread Plc (WTB)  Chief Executive
Officer Andy Harrison said the company has no plans to spin off
its Costa coffee chain and the focus is on growing the business.  “We are 100 percent focused on growing Costa,” Harrison
said in a conference call with reporters today. “There are no
plans to spin it out.” Harrison also said the U.K. hotel market
remains “challenging” and he envisages the economy being
little changed for the next year.  To contact the reporter on this story:
